@page "/policies"

<PageTitle>Policies - SmartBite</PageTitle>

<div class="container py-5 anim-fade-in" style="max-width: 800px;">
    <div class="text-center mb-5">
        <h1 class="fw-bold" style="color: #24292f;">SmartBite Policies</h1>
        <p class="text-muted">Your privacy and security are our top priorities.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 mb-4" style="background-color: #fff;">
        <div class="card-body p-4">
            <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 d-flex align-items-center">
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="me-2 text-primary" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
                Privacy Policy
            </h4>
            <p class="text-muted small mb-2">Last Updated: October 2023</p>
            <p>At SmartBite, we take your personal data seriously. We only collect the information necessary to provide you with tailored diet plans, shopping lists, and AI coach recommendations. We do not sell your personal data to third parties.</p>

            <h6 class="fw-bold mt-4">Data Collection</h6>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Log Data:</strong> Meals, calories, and hydration logs.</li>
                <li><strong>Account Info:</strong> Username and basic profile metadata.</li>
                <li><strong>AI Prompts:</strong> Sent to GitHub Models securely strictly for generating wellness advice.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 mb-4" style="background-color: #fff;">
        <div class="card-body p-4">
            <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 d-flex align-items-center">
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="me-2 text-primary" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/></svg>
                Terms of Service
            </h4>
            <p>By using SmartBite, you agree to our terms of use. SmartBite is a tool to assist with diet tracking and shopping lists. The AI Coach provides general wellness advice and is <strong>not</strong> a substitute for professional medical care.</p>
            <p>Users must be at least 13 years old to use the platform. Any misuse, automation of the API limits, or harassment in the community areas will lead to account termination.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .anim-fade-in {
        animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in-out;
    }
    @@keyframes fadeIn {
        from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
        to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
</style>
